Package birdgame

Class GamePiece

  • java.lang.Object
    • birdgame.GamePiece
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Food, Player
    public class GamePiece
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    GamePiece contains various attributes of a GamePiece, including x-location, y-location, x and y increment, width, height, and type; in addition, the GamePiece class contains a move() method that defines how each GamePiece moves on the screen
